><ingested> 1692773925</ingested><modified> 2023-08-23T06:58:49+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[Sports & Recreation]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Mariella Moon]]></category><media:content height="1047" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/a3086a30-4179-11ee-bfb6-76d478670016" width="1600"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1047" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/a3086a30-4179-11ee-bfb6-76d478670016" width="1600"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Blizzard Entertainment]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Graphic rendering of a vampire child with fangs and glowing eyes.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Diablo IV]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[‘Hyper Light Breaker’ early access pushed back to early 2024]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/hyper-light-breaker-announcement-trailer-201547113.html"><em>《Hyper Light Breaker》</em></a>是一款动作 Rogue-lite 游戏，原定于今年秋季进入 Steam 抢先体验版，现已第二次推迟。 2016 年<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2019-07-25-rpg-hyper-light-drifter-pixel-2d-ios.html"><em>《Hyper Light Drifter》</em></a>的精神继承者的发布窗口现已重新安排在 2024 年初。</p><p>开发商 Heart Machine 的创始人兼创意总监 Alx Preston 在宣布推迟的<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://youtu.be/InuOjewX_-s">视频</a>中表示：“因此，在推出抢先体验之前，我们还需要在<em>《Hyper Light Breaker》</em>上多花一点时间。” “这意味着我们将把日期推迟到明年初，即 2024 年。”他表示，额外的时间将“让我们能够充分发挥游戏的潜力。”普雷斯顿感谢粉丝们的耐心和支持，并承诺“一场新的冒险将不辜负粉丝们对《心脏机器》游戏的期望。” </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/3584d8a0-4128-11ee-b9bc-05e8141f84a5" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/3584d8a0-4128-11ee-b9bc-05e8141f84a5" style="height:2160px;width:3840px;" alt="即将推出的游戏“Hyper Light Breaker”的宣传照。一个角色沿着建筑物的废墟冲浪，准备从末端跳下去。背景中可以看到沙漠地形和废墟。" data-uuid="7b1d6b01-1767-3575-b895-abee03c0e144"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">心脏机器/齿轮箱出版</div></figure><p><em>Hyper Light Breaker</em>将游戏玩法从 2D 转变为 3D，同时最多可添加三名玩家进行合作游戏。虽然 2016 年的原创游戏沿用了经典自上而下的塞尔达传说游戏的元素，但即将推出的开放世界游戏也融入了一些<em>《荒野之息》的</em>基础知识。其中包括探索散布着废墟的开阔乡村，同时乘坐滑翔机在空中翱翔和从山上冲浪。然而， <em>《Hyper Light Breaker》</em>使用程序生成的环境，这应该有助于提高可重玩性。它的战斗似乎也与任天堂的现代塞尔达游戏<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.gameinformer.com/exclusive-video/2023/04/11/meet-hyper-light-breakers-last-master-miniboss-with-director-alx-preston">不同</a>。 <a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/first-hyper-light-breaker-gameplay-trailer-reveals-fall-early-access-release-161516775.html">游戏的第一个预告片</a>让您可以近距离了解。</p><p> “我们有很多疯狂的想法想要融入到游戏中，这是令人兴奋和兴奋的，因为我们创建的格式和技术允许如此多的可能性，”普雷斯顿说。 “这一短暂的推动将为我们提供最好的机会，以便在明年的抢先体验开放开发中迈出更强有力的第一步。” </p><div id="1833d50599c44430a7b77dc96d2b6f5f"><iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/InuOjewX_-s" title="YouTube 视频播放器" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/hyper-light-breaker-early-access-pushed-back-to-early-2024-205056875.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/hyper-light-breaker-early-access-pushed-back-to-early-2024-205056875.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 407aad10-a8f0-45a4-b490-c5b1d7095e8d</guid><dc:creator>威尔·尚克林</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Tue, 22 Aug 2023 20:50:56 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1692736598</ingested><modified> 2023-08-22T20:36:42+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Will Shanklin]]></category><media:content height="2160" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/f9ff4450-4127-11ee-9f7e-8ecd39d005c8" width="3840"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2160" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/f9ff4450-4127-11ee-9f7e-8ecd39d005c8" width="3840"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Heart Machine / Gearbox Publishing]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Marketing still from the upcoming game ‘Hyper Light Breaker.’ A humanoid character with a red body and long blue hair gazes at a forboding red sky with purple beams coming down from the clouds.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Hyper Light Breaker]]></media:title></media:content></item></channel></rss>